<HEADLINE>
MASTERS OF JERSEY? WALL ST. SHUDDERS AT LIFE ACROSS THE RIVER. 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(bl) 
 By CHARLES V. BAGLI   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
