<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-07 13:39 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6516 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BOOKS-FICTION-BOS &LR;      12-07 0971
