<P>
   MARKET (New York) _ At midday, the industrial average was up 19
points and the Nasdaq index up 24 points. Elsewhere, prices rose
0.6 percent in Tokyo and 4.7 percent in Hong Kong. They fell 1.7
percent in Frankfurt but rose 0.4 percent in London. They gained
1.7 percent in Brazil but fell half a percent in Mexico. On the
American debt market, the long bond was up 13/32 point, with the
yield at 5.02 percent.
</P>
