<HEADER>
A6634 &Cx1f; taf-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FASHION-NYT-BUDGET &LR;      12-07 0134
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FASHION-NYT-BUDGET </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Fashion stories from The New York Times News Service for
 &UR; TUESDAY &LR; , Dec. 8.
</P>
<P>
