<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-07 15:12 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6729 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SOCIAL-DECISIONS-BOS &LR;      12-07 1458
