</P>
<P>
   MEANS-COLUMN (Washington) _ First Lady Hillary Rodham Clinton
gives a tour of the festively decorated White House as President
Clinton prepares for a symposium on Social Security. There is an
air of unreality at the White House as they carry on as though
nothing of importance is happening in the congressional impeachment
process. By MARIANNE MEANS.
