   A color illustration, free to clients, is available via e-mail
or the NewsCom website (www.newscom.com). The username of the site
is ``nytdemo''. Call 212-499-3342 for the current password, or
leave a voice-mail message with your e-mail address and the photo
will be sent to you. On the site, the photo is under the headings:
NYT Syndicate/LifeBeat Photos, and is slugged ``poetry project.''
