<P>
   All the quotations in this quiz are wrapped in the vast array of
Christmas experience _ the songs, the stories, the cinema and the
overall spirit of the ``most wonderful time of the year.''
</P>
<P>
   (Slugged: BC--CHRISTMAS-QUOTATIONS-LIFEBEAT-NYTSF, priority code
r, category code l) &QL;
