</P>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ Like all good shows, the Museum of Modern Art's
``Jackson Pollock'' asks more questions than it answers. But it
does lay one to rest: Is there more to the controversial American
than ``Jack the Dripper''? The answer is a resounding ``Yes!'' By
JANET TYSON. Story will move in ``e'' entertainment category.
(Accompanied by POLLOCK-OTHERS and POLLOCK-ELSEWHERE.) &QL; 
