reading the snipings of overpaid celebrities. OK, many things get
you in the spirit better than that, but there's something about
celebrity-sniping that's just plain dirty fun. Two recently
published books celebrate this. By ROBERT PHILPOT. Story will move
in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
