<DOCNO> NYT19981207.0245 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-07 17:06 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6971 &Cx1f; tad-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-WHITEHOUSE-HOLIDAY120     12-07 0619
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-WHITEHOUSE-HOLIDAY1208-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    FIRST LADY UNVEILS WHITE HOUSE DECORATIONS
 &HT;    PHOTOS to accompany this story are being placed in the National
folder on the Cox server.
 &HT;    EDS: Moving both in Washington (w) and Lifestyle (l) categories.
 &HT;    550 words
 &HT;    
 &HT;    By BOB DART
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service
