<HEADLINE>
&HT;    
 &HT;    GATES: TRUSTBUSTERS SEEK TO DESTROY MICROSOFT
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    740 words
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON -- Bill Gates charged the government Monday with
seeking to ruin Microsoft Corp. in court by coming to the aid of
its business rivals.
</P>
