</P>
<P>
   NETWATCH _ ATLANTA _ Online auctions prove one of the basic
truths of human nature: one person's trash is another person's
treasure. The Web auction game is relatively new, and might be a
little too much for Web surfers just getting comfortable with
online shopping. Still, if you read the directions carefully and
ignore the $250 Furby's, (unless the money is going to charity) you
can find your own personal pot of gold _ or gold plate_ at an
online auction. (Katz, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED
