at least one article of impeachment is growing partly because some
swing-vote Republicans are comfortable there is little chance the
Senate would vote to convict President Clinton. By Michael Kranish.
</P>
<P>
   IMPEACH-LAWYERS (Washington) -- Clinton aides and lawyers are
