<P>
   &UR; SPORTS (s) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   FBN-REPLAY (Undated) -- The use of instant replay in NFL games,
which ended after the 1991 season, is back in the spotlight again
after a recent rash of controversial on-field officiating calls. By
Kevin Paul Dupont. 900 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
