   Arkansas 0-0 6-3 did not play Today at SW Missouri
</P>
<P>
   South Carolina 0-1 6-1 did not play Dec. 17 vs. Clemson
</P>
<P>
   Vanderbilt 0-1 3-3 did not pay Dec. 19 at Indiana
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
