<P>
   (NYT22) SEA BRIGHT BEACH, N.J. -- Dec. 7, 1998
--WARM-WEATHER-FLOATER, 12-07 -- Mario Orriols does some sunbathing
on the beach as a woman in the background walks her dogs by the
shoreline. The temperature just 18 days before Christmas reached a
balmy 75 degrees Fahrenheit. (Dith Pran/New York Times Photo) *LITE
</P>
