<P>
   (NYT5) NEW YORK -- Dec. 7, 1998 -- PEARL-HARBOR-FLOATER, 12-07
-- In memory of those who died during the Japanse assault on Pearl
Harbor, pilots from Long Island, flying World War II vintage
aircraft, fly past the Statue of Liberty after dropping roses.
Fifty-seven years ago the Japanese launched a surprise attack on
