<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BOLSHOI-RESTORATION-RESEND-INDEPENDENT-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
BOLSHOI THEATRE RESTORATION APPEAL LAUNCHED  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (RESENDING from Fri., Dec. 4)   (This 600-word ``separate buy'' article is from The Independent
newspaper in London.)  
  
 (To publish this article, it must be purchased from New York Times
Syndicate sales representative NIRDI RELIS in New York at
1-800-972-3550 or 212-499-3333, or fax her at 212-499-3382.)  
  
 (PLEASE NOTE: This article has been transmitted twice _ into the
``a'' domestic/general news and ``t'' travel news files.)  
  
 By HELEN WOMACK  
 c.1998 The Independent, London  
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features)  
<TEXT>
